 with a high degree\nof self-similarity, spanning about 8 orders of magnitude in scale size, down to\nscales of order 10 m.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Mar 2009 03:14:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
